{
  "page": "Feature quote/107",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Sometimes, the best thing you can do is nothing. When I first came to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, I was hurt whenever <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Ned</a> went to the <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood\" title=\"Godswood\">godswood</a> to sit beneath his <a href=\"/index.php/Heart_tree\" title=\"Heart tree\">heart tree</a>. Part of his soul was in that tree, I knew, a part I would never share. Yet without that part, I soon realized, he would not have been Ned. <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Westerling\" title=\"Jeyne Westerling\">Jeyne</a>, child, you have wed the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>, as I did... and in the north, the winters will come.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Tully\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Catelyn Tully\">Catelyn Tully</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_20\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 20\">Chapter 20</a>, Catelyn III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404124307\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 73/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 426/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighe